# Test file for Movement API endpoints
# Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or similar tools

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5241/api/Movement/Health

### Get Current Position
GET http://localhost:5241/api/Movement/Position

### Test Small X Movement
POST http://localhost:5241/api/Movement/Command
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "move",
  "axis": "X",
  "direction": "positive",
  "stepSize": "small"
}

